p.k: It's touch-and-go when sanctuary lothario, Randy, succumbs to an infection, a new arrival gets a presidential welcome and Becky unravels the secrets of sloth attraction
The sanctuary team try to save a poisoned sloth, Claire turns sloth sleuth to find a much-loved missing toy, and Becky tries to pin down the secret of sloth manliness
78% Jeff, a photographer who lives and works out of his home, is at risk of losing his business and his assistant because of his blood-thirsty cat, Buster
78% Maryam is a pet psychic, but she can't communicate with her vicious cat Lily. Plus, Khloe discovers an entire feral colony behind her parent's house
Earl returns from rehab, hoping to rebuild his life working with the dogs. Plus, Lizzy rescues a dog after a confrontation with the owner who abandoned it
A woman travels from San Diego to offer one of Villalobos' senior dogs a home. Meanwhile, Lizzy and Marcel search for a mama dog's lost puppies out in the country
The team creates a circus-themed enclosure for bearded dragon, Nash. Jason helps Greg with a surprise party and suggests bringing his tarantula
Robert and Indah, a Komodo dragon, participate in an exciting research experiment. Terri tries to save a koala joey with a zero percent chance of survival
As Bindi celebrates her 21st birthday, she gets a surprise proposal from her boyfriend. Meanwhile, things get dangerous as Robert wrangles gators in thick mud
74% The Raneys arrives at a homestead threatened by heat, coyotes and even cows. Disaster strikes when Marty attempts to protect livestock with a massive build
Returning from Puerto Rico, Amanda sets out to acclimatize her rescues to life on the mainland. First, a trip to the vet to make sure the dogs are in good health
Amanda goes undercover to take in 3 dogs rescued from puppy mills, including a sweet chihuahua that steals the heart of one of her crew members
After the eruption of the Kilauea volcano in May 2018, shelters on Hawaii have been overrun with displaced animals. Amanda and her family embark on a humanitarian mission
Coyote is hunting for the deadly Sydney funnel web spider. Catching one is a dangerous endeavour, but a life-saving serum can be created from the venom
For a change of pace, Coyote is searching for some of Australia’s less dangerous and more adorable creatures, starting with the famous koala bear
Biologist and predator specialist Dave Salmoni journeys to a mountainous island in the North East Pacific, which is home to a large number of grizzly bears
78% Debbie is torn between her boyfriend and her peeing cat Blinkie. Krisi and Jason want to get married, but standing in their way is her crazy cat, Frankie
78% Ambreen has been in an abusive relationship for the past 13 years, but her abuser is her cat, Calvin. Can Jackson Galaxy help Ambreen to get her life back?
When Tia receives an adoption email unlike any other, she makes a cross-country trip to find a dog a home before Christmas. Plus, the family get an unforgettable gift
Tia is in Detroit helping a rescue facility at risk of closure. Villalobos looks for a stray pit bull nearby and a grieving adopter wants a dog to heal her heart
Dr. Michael Domeier attempts to find the mating waters of the Great White and where it gives birth, which until now has perplexed the scientific community
76% A mysterious outbreak leads to a four year old boy drowning in his own mucus, and a wound in a seven year old's knee has a vile cause
Sensitive sloth, Linus, hits a rocky patch when Claire has to leave the Sanctuary. Scientist Becky reveals which of the sloth species is a natural-born swimmer
Becky tries to find out what drives the females of the species wild. Meanwhile, young choloepus, Tigger, starts to display decidedly un-slothlike tendencies
How does a squirrel take on a dangerous rattle snake? What makes eagles’ eyes so powerful? Plus, why is the planet overrun with bugs? Experts answer these questions!
